Overview

This dashboard shows SCTP and Tunnel overview related to the Prisma Access Integration.

The dashboard is made to provide general statistics and show the ingested SCTP and Tunnel logs from Prisma Access.

It includes visualizations such as Top Actions Performed by Firewall, Source Packets, Destination Packets, and Total Packets, providing a comprehensive view of network traffic and activity. Additionally, it features Top SCTP Event Notification Type and Tunnel Event by Type, highlighting significant events and their distribution. For security analysis, the dashboard presents Top Associated URL Categories and Top Security Policy Rule, identifying common patterns and policies. Furthermore, it includes Top Reason for Session Termination, offering insights into session issues. Detailed views are available through Tunnel Event Essential Details and SCTP Event Essential Details
